# Document System Phase 3 Implementation Plan

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Dashboard API Fix
- **File**: [src/dashboard/dashboard.service.ts](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/dashboard/dashboard.service.ts)
- **Change**: Modify `totalTemplates` to count uniquely by `templateCode` instead of just [count()](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/users/repositories/users.repository.ts#24-27).

### 2. Users CRUD
- **API**: Add endpoints (`POST /api/users`, `PUT /api/users/:id`, `DELETE /api/users/:id`) in [UsersController](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/users/users.controller.ts#5-15) and [UsersService](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/users/users.service.ts#8-66).
- **UI**: Update [Users.tsx](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system-ui/src/pages/Users.tsx) to include an "Add User" modal and "Edit" / "Suspend" actions that hit the API.

### 3. Application Clients CRUD
- **API**: Add endpoints (`PUT /api/clients/:id`, `DELETE /api/clients/:id`, `POST /api/clients/:id/rotate`) in [ClientsController](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/clients/clients.controller.ts#7-30).
- **UI**: Update [AppClients.tsx](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system-ui/src/pages/AppClients.tsx) to include "Create App" modal, "Edit" modal, and "Delete" / "Rotate Secret" actions.

### 4. Version Timeline Manager Redesign
- **UI Component**: Restructure [VersionTimelineManager.tsx](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system-ui/src/components/VersionTimelineManager.tsx).
  - Display a single horizontal timeline track.
  - Show blocks of color mapped to their time.
  - Below/beside the timeline, show a list of all versions (including historical).
  - Add buttons: `[Remove from timeline]` (nullifies dates), `[Delete]` (deletes from DB, disabled if in timeline), `[Edit]` (opens editor).
- **API Logic**: Add `DELETE /api/templates/:id` to support the deletion of unused versions.

## Verification
- Verify Dashboard template count accurately reflects unique templates.
- Verify User and AppClient CRUD operations reflect in the database.
- Verify Timeline redesign acts as a unified track and allows deleting/linking versions.
